This area is designed to showcase the capabilities and limitations of the quest systems. In various locations throughout this area, you will find examples of the different types of quests the system can handle.  

Information on the quest type can be garnered by examining the sign near each questing area.  To assign a quest, left-click on the sign and a conversation will begin which allows you to assign or unassign the quests for that area.

Once you complete all the quests in each area, return to this location and talk to the young lady here.  She will send you on a quest throughout the area that combines multiple quest types, culminating in an escort quest.
Welcome to the Quest System Discovery Area!
